==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Three feet of ice is not the result of one cold day.

===Pronunciation===
*[[Pinyin]]: bīng dòng sān chǐ, fēi yī rì zhī hán

===Proverb===
'''[[冰]][[凍]][[三]][[尺]]，[[非]][[一]][[日]][[之]][[寒]]'''

# [[Rome wasn't built in a day]].

===Alternate forms===
[[冰冻三尺，非一日之寒]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

